<img class="img-fluid o_we_custom_image" src="https://odoo.belsis.com.tr/web/image/4977-68e133b7/dogum_gunu.png?access_token=f2ae0f14-ed22-4364-810b-79a2ff461aa8" width="190" height="267" style="border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;display:inline-block;height:auto;max-width:100%;vertical-align:middle;">
<br></p>
